user_instruction: 'Tell Jane to send an email to me (info@rainbowfertility.com) with the details we need for our consultation. Ask her to check her Notion for information.'

formatted_items.content:
Hi Jane,

I hope you’re doing well!  
When you have a moment, could you please email us at info@rainbowfertility.com with the details we’ll need to set up your initial consultation? You can find a checklist of the required information in your Notion workspace.

Thank you so much, and we look forward to hearing from you!

Warm regards,  
Rainbow Fertility Care
